surface-sow
Homonym Number:
Word Class:verb
Sense Number: 1
Definition:to sow seed on the surface of soil so that it germinates there, rather than being tilled.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
